- The <hi rend="underline">same appearances,</hi> are almost<lb/>
uniformly exhibited, &amp; the most<lb/>
accurate &amp; perspicuous accounts<lb/>
that have ever been given of a<lb/>
volcanic fire, are those of the<lb/>
